lation [\u2026] both on a regional and national basis\u201d (page 191). Mr. de lind van Wijngaarden emphasised the fol- lowing key MSM", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6d54ec39-5e3c-4cfe-b4fb-1083a68c011b": {"__data__": {"id_": "6d54ec39-5e3c-4cfe-b4fb-1083a68c011b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/developing-comprehensive-package-services-reduce-hiv-among-men-who-have-sex-men-msm-and-transgender-tg-populations-asia-and", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Developing a Comprehensive Package of Services to Reduce HIV among Men who have Sex with Men (MSM) and Transgender (TG) Populations in Asia and the Pacific - Regional Consensus Meeting Report", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/developing-comprehensive-package-services-reduce-hiv-among-men-who-have-sex-men-msm-and-transgender-tg-populations-asia-and", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e2d3af4eb1fa98f4ecf2670d025b7c777416f25572efd6ef0c2d0a0b70fc52c7"}, "3": {"node_id": "96d75b81-8e36-4e30-b875-675a84d8bcef", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/developing-comprehensive-package-services-reduce-hiv-among-men-who-have-sex-men-msm-and-transgender-tg-populations-asia-and", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "28ba82801ee6f6be13d5aead705e6dbfd8e9971bde03fdf915f9ad87a0ecbaa7"}}, "hash": "225281005ce8ab85d7a54d82750177f4fd0184