ient maturity to understand the benefits, risks and social implications of such a disclosure; and ii) the child has no parent or care- giver and there is no designated child protection organisation arranging the placement of the child; or e) a children\u2019s court, if - i) consent in terms of paragraph (a), (b), (c) or (d) is unreasonably withheld and disclosure is in the best interests of the child; or ii) the child or the parent or care- giver of the child is incapable of giving consent.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "36cddea2-ad1b-45f3-8feb-dc8858fb7f8e": {"__data__": {"id_": "36cddea2-ad1b-45f3-8feb-dc8858fb7f8e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/enabling-effective-responses-hiv-pacific-island-countries-drafting-instructions-human-rights-based-legislative-reform", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Enabling Effective Responses to HIV in Pacific Island Countries: Drafting Instructions for Human rights-based Legislative Reform", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/enabling-effective-responses-hiv-pacific-island-countries-drafting-instructions-human-rights-based-legislative-reform", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "73efafb25aff229678167e9a4a2f8d96afad63626b6371d4f8feddfbfbce4f81"}, "2": {"node_id": "a962c9d4-5f8c-4168-873f-9412770f46c6", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/enabling-effective-responses-hiv-pacific-island-countries-drafting-instructions-human-r